Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:51.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:56.38,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To keep on living,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:01:59.55,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:29.49,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:31.25,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:44.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It has begun, Mr. Shiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:47.68,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This has been my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:53.77,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This plot you've written will betray you in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:58.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your curtain call will be ugly, I would say... Scythe Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:01.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That would be simply fun as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:06.10,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You may sing and dance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:11.39,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}soldiers of my creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.38,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Spilling your blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:17.36,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and killing each other in a world gone mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.20,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}These girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:13.26,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There could only be one person with such warped taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:16.28,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:19.46,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are still at least two enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.97,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The odds don't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:22.28,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:28.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't think Inferno brought more than these girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:36.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He wouldn't let useless extras be lifted onto the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:40.21,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He wants to close the curtain himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:44.38,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:55.83,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Neun and Fünf have left the stage, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:58.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You fought fairly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:01.26,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The scenario is better than anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.46,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the perfect adornment for the epilogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:13.20,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be the decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.95,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Use the distraction to look for Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:22.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we get to their commander, we will have the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:26.43,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You are the only one who can read his moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:31.89,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.38,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:55.20,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Two versus one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.49,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.22,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.14,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:25.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Welcome to my stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:44.17,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't perform on your stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:57.62,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Only two of them are coming at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:59.85,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are the others after Ein?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:09.61,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Surely you're not surrendering, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:14.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No. I've come to kill you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:16.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.24,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:21.15,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.74,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In a situation as ridden with despair as this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:26.55,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}how do you intend to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:33.14,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't be killed here in your storyboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:38.46,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You would never allow such a childish ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:44.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I never thought you would gain such insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:47.10,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's just as you have said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:50.19,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I returned to this Island Country...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:54.53,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...because I want to enjoy my little girls' performance with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:57.93,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:07:59.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sechs and Sieben.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:03.22,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They deserve no less as your little sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:03.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:09.15,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's Ein, the sample you are based on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:10.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Go play with her for a little while,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:13.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and when she reaches her limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:17.35,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}cut her into tiny pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:49.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong, Ein? You're up against a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:53.56,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You present me with this childish end even though I went easy on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:55.34,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You are a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:36.34,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Their execution, movement, and breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:43.22,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...are the same as mine were.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:50.19,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, ever since you created me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:57.07,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}nothing has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:31.42,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry I had to rely on you to the very end, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:49.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:51.86,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm astonished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:56.32,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I never thought you would still be able to show me such fighting strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.58,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:01.78,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've come here to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:05.18,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I doubt that will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:06.16,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:08.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because I surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:16.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:22.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You see, I'm no longer a threat to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:27.47,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How about it? Can you kill me now, Ein?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:33.12,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the difference between you and Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:36.31,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Unlike Zwei who fights of his own will,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:40.90,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you can only kill when you are under orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:43.09,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you were to abandon that tenet,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:45.84,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}your soul would shatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:49.49,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A murderer's fear and guilt would haunt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:54.26,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The mind you have, bereft of force of will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:56.38,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...is weaker than that of an ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.64,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You cannot shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:06.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In fact, you never could.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.23,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:11.72,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:20.05,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was truly entertained tonight, Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:24.78,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:32.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You really are a foolish man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:36.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You honestly think you can cold-read people's minds...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:43.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:46.51,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because I... despise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:55.89,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And also... because I can't forgive you for hurting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:59.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What will happen to you after you have killed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You will keep on running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.77,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...without your memories ever coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:07.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All you enter is an endless spiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That may be true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:14.37,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...I will kill you, Scythe Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:16.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.92,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is amazing, Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:23.42,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't call me Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:26.16,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My name is Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:28.27,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By that I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:29.22,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and by that I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:31.72,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The muse's twisted prank...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:40.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Leave for hell ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:42.86,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll follow you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:45.62,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He will be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:22.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:23.93,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scythe Master and Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How will you proceed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:41.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The young will destroy the old system and erect a new one in its place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:43.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The transient flower withers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A ghost that never existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:50.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if the dream is fleeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:55.86,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}there are things we must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.72,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is this? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:06.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Apparently there was an incident at the chapel and the old schoolhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.46,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh my, that's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:21.96,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:24.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:33.42,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Helmut von Giuseppe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:35.20,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Born in Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:40.14,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He acquired a Ph.D. in neuroscience and psychology and researched a new treatment at his university.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:43.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He was widely known as an expert on interrogation and brainwashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:48.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At that time, he came in contact with the underworld while wandering from place to place,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:51.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and became the freelance middleman for assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:54.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The alias he used in the underworld...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:55.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...was Scythe Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In order to find Elen's past,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:03.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}we had to trace this man's career.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:06.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Her and Scythe's first meeting five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:10.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...marked the beginning of the life of "Ein".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Their encounter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:16.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...was in Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:18.03,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He came to this institution?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:24.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, about five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:29.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He told me he wanted to adopt a girl from Ulan Bator.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:32.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Adopt her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:35.47,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Her skin was so pale...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:39.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and she'd probably be your age now if she's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:43.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is it just my imagination or...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:46.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...did she look just like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ulan Bator.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:52.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We've come as far as Mongolia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:55.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen's trail goes cold here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:19:00.20,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look at the sky from the grassy vastness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:02.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That will give you certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:06.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll know when you look up at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:16.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you are a Mongolian,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:51.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you could never forget its sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:57.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The sky and the clouds are always inside your blood and bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:19:59.71,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll know when you look up at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:11.23,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We don't need to search any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:13.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:16.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.47,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can remember this sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I dreamed about it from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:26.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though I've made lots of mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:51.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and failed to keep many promises in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}there is one promise I must keep no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:58.35,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing is necessary any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:02.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if I couldn't find anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:05.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have a name you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:10.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will make you smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:17.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have memories of the time we spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:21.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will give you back your true smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:24.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:26.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:42.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's all I need...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:47.86,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's all I need to keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:52.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all I need.
